♫  I don't want to have a tiring talk today  ♫

919
01:06:23,864 --> 01:06:25,944
♫  Dance with me  ♫

920
01:06:25,944 --> 01:06:29,894
 The moment Pil Sung marries into that family, he'll become a chaebol's son-in-law. 

921
01:06:29,894 --> 01:06:31,754
 How he feels is important. 

922
01:06:31,754 --> 01:06:35,834
 If he likes Ma Ri, it'd happen. But if he doesn't, it won't. 

923
01:06:35,834 --> 01:06:39,294
 Is Pil Sung dating the lady in the rental unit, by chance? 

924
01:06:39,294 --> 01:06:43,074
 Why is Pil Sung coming out of her room at this early hour? 

925
01:06:43,074 --> 01:06:44,584
 We need to talk. 

926
01:06:44,584 --> 01:06:46,364
 Why did you come out of President Gong's car? 

927
01:06:46,364 --> 01:06:49,444
 Don't eat with him. Don't see him privately, either! 

